      Hard to read.

      Aug 7, 2024 | Breeann | Verified Buyer

      The font is too small and hard to read on the speckled back color. I also have a type on a phone number, but that is my fault, so I will need to reorder. At least I will know to increase the font size.

      Response from Vistaprint Customer Care Team:

      Thank you for your feedback. We’re sorry to hear that the font size and readability of the business cards you received did not meet your expectations. For your reorder, increasing the font size to 2-3 points should improve readability on the speckled background. Should you have any further inquiries or require assistance in the future, please feel free to reach out to us.
